reviewText: This movie was poorly directed, poorly acted and looked like someone's home movie. The characters made no sense, the acting was terrible, the actors were horribly unattractive- especially the ugly guy w/ rotten teeth and no talent. Avoid this "film"- if you can even call this home movie w/ no talent or intelligence at all. A waste of this lesbians time. Gracias losers!
I can think of better movies to pass the time with.  I understand and accept that it is a corny film, and there were some good moments.  But I wouldn't watch it a second time

Some FANTASTIC singing in "POP-U-larity!", who knew?

Some not-so-great singing too... oh well... it's a small town, yo!

The "Darque" character and Hippie-Healer girl were funny.
